channel.title: SAS || Old school || Unique || Alot of Features [ 2006/2005 ]
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i.imgur.com/8TrHF.png[/img][/CENTER]
[font=courier new][SIZE=20pt]hello and welcome to me thread/ Project. I am making this in the spare time i have basically to waste time :), It will be a old school server set about 2005/2006. It will not have any custom items but will have allot of custom features. if you would like to join the developement team just send me a pm, currently it is just me working on the project :D, note that you must have a decent java knowledge and you must speak English, You must be not be a new member of rune|server and have to be slightly trusted. So anyway less of me explainig and i will give you the features :D so i hope you enjoy it, remember to hit the "thanks" button :P, note that i will keep on updating this thread.[/SIZE][/font]
[font=Times New Roman][SIZE=60pt][COLOR=navy][u]Join development team[/u][/COLOR][/SIZE][/font] [code] how you work with others ( mood, humor ect.ect ): Skype or msn: java knowledge ( out of 10 ): Proof: Age: Why you want to join: Why we should pick you: [/code]
[font=Times New Roman][SIZE=60pt][COLOR=navy][u]Bug fixes[/u][/COLOR][/SIZE][/font]
[ul][li]When clickin spell then on npc , you do the spell and run to them[/li] [li]Npc's wouldnt walk to you when you are diagonal from object's[/li] [li]Fixed a few npc's animations[/li] [li]when drop dharoks it resets your timer to 0[/li] [li]Dharok's axe disapears when turns to "0"[/li] [li]Degrading messages thx to Eliminate[/li] [li]All barrows items turn to "0" when dropped[/li] [li]when dharok's axe 25 vanishes you still have bonuses[/li] [li]Dharok's axe animation's[/li] [li]Dharok's axe levels required[/li] [li]Dharok's axe speed[/li][/ul]
[font=Times New Roman][SIZE=60pt][COLOR=navy][u]Update log[/u][/COLOR][/SIZE][/font]
[ul][li]Added random event tree spirit[/li] [li]Rewrote Item Requirments system[/li] [li]Rewrote some combat [/li] [li]Flawless Switching[/li] [li]Added woodcutting System[/li] [li]Double door system and single doors[/li] [li]Can pick xp rates on start[/li] [li]Degrading System[/li][/ul]
[font=Times New Roman][SIZE=60pt][COLOR=navy][u]Skills & Combat[/u][/COLOR][/SIZE][/font] [img]http://i50.tinypic.com/28bv8dl.png[/img][font=Times New Roman][SIZE=40pt][COLOR=blue]Melee[/COLOR][/SIZE][/font]
